          <mainBody>
            <p eId="annex_1_p_8"><b>Annex A - Territorial extent and application in the United Kingdom</b></p>
            <blockContainer>
              <num>31 </num>
              <p>The Act extends to England and Wales but applies in England only, save for the consequential amendments to other enactments, which have the same extent as the provisions being amended.</p>
            </blockContainer>
          </mainBody>
